      "id": "PopularPost90516",
      "post_content": "I actually find this better than [Wall of Fire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wall of Fire). Sure, its base stats may be less impressive, but if you have extra mana, it can take a bigger beating. Firebreathing really doesn't help a wall.  \n  \nSide note: Jaya Ballard has all the best flavor text.",
